        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Cafe Hon</h2>
            <p>Cafe Hon is a charming rooftop cafe located in the heart of Hanoi, Vietnam. Perched high above the city, it offers breathtaking panoramic views of the Ho Chi Minh Mausoleum and the bustling streets below. Whether you're sipping coffee, enjoying local delicacies, or watching the sunset, Cafe Hon is the perfect spot to relax and take in the beauty of Hanoi.</p>
            <p>Open daily from 7 AM to 10 PM. Address: 30 P. Lê Thái Tổ, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội, Vietnam.</p>
        </section>

